'''Sentinel beetles''' were beetles used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Placed around their slave cities, the beetles would begin to flap their wings and create a steady drone whenever there was an escape attempt or an intruder. That way, they would alert nearby [[Warrior caste|Yuuzhan Vong warriors]] who would then "deal" with the problem. They were similar to [[Grutchin#Turfhopper|turfhoppers]].

